@338  = ~Ah, almost forgot! One last thing: a friend of mine is repairing my combat chainmail. It has good resistance and I think it will come in handy against magic users. We will find him in an abandoned house to the northwest of the Athkatla Docks. When we have some time, I would like us to head there.~

