@3284  = ~I understand, <CHARNAME>... Revenge does not stir my heart, although confronting the orcs may prevent innocent deaths.~
@3285  = ~If that doesn't move you, perhaps you'd prefer to face him simply to prove your own strength or perhaps to seize his treasure.~
@3286  = ~Hm, now that you mention it, we could use a good fight to blow off some steam.. Go on.~
@3287  = ~You're right about potential victims, Dusk. I'm sorry. Tell me more.~
@3288  = ~I care very little for your problems, man. I'm the one in charge here.~
@3289  = ~So be it, <CHARNAME>. I won't press you on this matter. If fortune is on our side, Alabarza may still be there when you decide to investigate the matter...~
@3290  = ~Demolisher, return to your master and tell him we'll go when we're able.~
@3291  = ~To the point, Mathyus. I'm sure you have something... interesting to tell, don't you?~
@3292  = ~I knew it... It can't be anyone other than Alabarza the Mutilator.~
