@3300  = ~Well, it's a little scary to me.~
@3301  = ~You're right, Dusk. Taking them down will be a piece of cake.~
@3302  = ~*whisper* Dang it, <CHARNAME>, don't be a coward. If you have doubts, send me to the front lines. I'll do the dirty work.~
@3303  = ~That's the spirit, <CHARNAME>!~
@3304  = ~Mathyus! Give me the location of this clan. <CHARNAME> and I will take care of destroying it completely.~
