@3313  = ~Bastard! I can imagine the hate that must be running inside you, Dusk.~
@3314  = ~I suppose it would be logical to think that the desire for revenge could take hold of me, <CHARNAME>. And I must admit that I am holding back my anger at the moment... But that is not the answer.~
