@3327  = ~And it's obvious, Dusk. These guys must belong to a Gossiping Order more than a Mage Order.~
@3328  = ~I'm not even offended anymore that my secret is out, Dusk. Nevertheless, I'm interested in knowing who this sorcerer is and what the hell he's doing here.~
