@3335  = ~*Dusk approaches the creature's corpse and pierces the still-beating heart with the crimson sword*~
@3336  = ~Ha! I was right, <CHARNAME>. The crimson sword has improved... I feel the heat of the hells in its hilt... and it doesn't even affect me.~
@3337  = ~Excellent, Dusk. I trust you'll use it for the benefit of the party.~
@3338  = ~Dusk, be careful or the sword will dominate you.~
@3339  = ~I'll use it for the malefaction of our enemies, <CHARNAME>. Let's go... Alabarza is waiting for us.~
@3340  = ~My will is mine, <CHARNAME>. Have faith... I won't be dominated by a piece of steel. Now, let's go... Alabarza is waiting for us.~

