@3359  = ~*Suddenly, a dazzling scarlet light emanates from Dusk's eyes*~
@3360  = ~And so ends the days of the Shilmista ranger...~
@3361  = ~<CHARNAME>, Apologies. I didn't warn you beforehand of what I was going to do. Let's just say... I didn't want to involve you.~
