@3369  = ~Its energy comes from the Pandemonium, a plane that serves as a refuge for demons and shadows.~
@3370  = ~The orb draws its power from a creature from that plane. Over time, since I absorbed its power, I have been able to clarify my communication with it. There was something in our plane of existence that was preventing its... resurgence.~
