@3372  = ~And now we shall come to know it...~
@3373  = ~Very well, Danctian. Make the blade of Cormyr fearsome to my enemies!~
@3374  = ~Very well, Danctian. Let my armor become my defense against those I must bring to execution!~


@3375  = ~"Just the goods, bare and..." *stops writing as everyone turns their attention to him*~
@3376  = ~Uh... Sorry, Ribald sir, it's just that you have a way with words when it comes to this stuff. And I thought I could learn a thing or two from your speech.~

