@3390  = ~Irenicus! You will pay for the deaths you have caused in the Waukeen's Promenade. The deaths of the innocent will not be forgotten. For Cormyr!~
@3391  = ~Finally! The disgusting sorcerer is within our reach, <CHARNAME>. Let's show this fool what real power is!~
@3392  = ~Dusk, the warrior of Cormyr. His heart has hardened, but it has made him more powerful. His gaze is cold and fearless; yet his eyes emit respect in your presence.~
