@3423  = ~A strange place for the final confrontation against this Order of iblith. Don't worry, abbil, the strength of Shar is with us.~
@3424  = ~Hmm... I think we've been here before. This is like some kind of déjà vu, don't you think, Dusk? I once went through something similar when that bootlicker Trax kept coming over and over again to hassle me about selling illegal turnips in the Government District. 'Gnome, you can't sell that here. It's forbidden.' And that phrase was repeated practically every day.~
